

1. Barycentre ED analyzer (Based on CMSSW_10_6_12)

   read track alignment tags with different labels in ES and dump the barycentre for different substructures into trees

   cmsRun config
   - PixelBaryCentreAnalyzer_2016_cfg.py for 2016 (Phase-0)
   - PixelBaryCentreAnalyzer_2017+2018_cfg.py for 2017,2018 (Phase-1)

   hadd the output root file to get full Run-2 Ntuple : PixelBaryCentre_2016_2017_2018.root

2. Plotting script (Need CMSSW env better >= CMSSW_10_6_X)

   Input : PixelBaryCentre_2016_2017_2018.root and FronTier service
   Plot barycentres of Rereco, EOY and Prompt in one canvas and save
   Plot barycentre diff between Rereco and Prompt, EOY and Prompt and save in one canvas

   plotBaryCentre_VS_BeamSpot.py -h for help

   Options:
     -h, --help         show this help message and exit
     --usePixelQuality  whether use SiPixelQuality                  default False
     --showLumi         whether use integrated lumi as x-axis       default False
     --years            years to plot                               default 2016, 2017, 2018
     --substructures    substrcutures to plot                       default BPIX and PIX

     ROOT options
     -l
     -q
     -b

     For 2016 alone, 
     python plotBaryCentre_VS_BeamSpot.py --showLumi --years 2016
     For 2017 alone,
     python plotBaryCentre_VS_BeamSpot.py --showLumi --years 2017     
     For 2018 alone,
     python plotBaryCentre_VS_BeamSpot.py --showLumi --years 2018

     Three years 
     python plotBaryCentre_VS_BeamSpot.py --showLumi --years 2016 2017 2018

     Only plot BPIX
     python plotBaryCentre_VS_BeamSpot.py --showLumi --years 2016 2017 2018 --substructure BPIX

    

